name: Solo
description:
Solo! 
This word has many meanings in my culture 
But one thing is clear to me from the word solo (Imprisonment)
Now it may be imprisoning a person's thoughts or overcoming his life

I have depicted some contradictions in this art!
 Tree means living inside a glass enclosure...

Your thoughts may be solitary like that glass case Look carefully, solitary confinement is an endless cycle 
It does not allow you to look back at the world around you and you are trapped inside your thoughts.
